data.description: Looks can be deceiving!  This property offers more than one can see from the outside.  4 bdrms, 2 bths living area and small dining area, efficiency kitchen nice size pantry super insulated house sits on 1 acre with a view of Gravel Hill valley.  There is 9 acres that adjoin this property that is nothing but pasture.  Master suite is 720 sq ft featuring a ceramic tiled walk in shower.  New pex water system 200 amp service, 2 HVAC's 2 water heaters EIFS (installed by certified dealer)  all over the outside, 8 security cameras Solar panels will convey.  Backyard is partially fenced with a tack room and a stall for your horse, goats or any other animal you might have!  This home has lots of sq footage for the price and an acre of ground surrounded by nothing but grass and trees for that added privacy.  Seller is motivated to sell!  Call for your showing TODAY
